  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">XPath queries that seem correct but return unexpected results are
  usually caused by the flat HTML structure that markdown-validator produces.
  Use the REPL to inspect the actual HTML and adjust your query.</shortdesc>

  <troublebody class="- topic/body troubleshooting/troublebody " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="troublebody:1;27:16">

    <condition id="condition" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/condition " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="condition:1;29:31">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="title:2;30:14">Situation</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:1;31:10">An XPath expression in a body rule returns no results, or it returns
      more elements than expected, causing the rule to behave incorrectly.</p>
    </condition>

    <troubleSolution class="- topic/bodydiv troubleshooting/troubleSolution " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="troubleSolution:1;35:22">
      <cause id="cause-flat-dom" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/cause " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="cause:1;36:34">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="title:3;37:16">Cause: Flat HTML — within-section containment does not work</title>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:2;38:12">The rendered HTML is flat: all headings are direct children of
        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;39:17">&lt;body&gt;</codeph>. Queries like
        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:2;40:17">.//h2[1]/following-sibling::p</codeph> do not return only
        paragraphs in the first H2's section — they return all paragraphs
        after the first H2, including those in every subsequent section.</p>
      </cause>
      <remedy id="remedy-flat-dom" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/remedy " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="remedy:1;44:36">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="title:4;45:16">Resolution</title>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="steps:1;46:16">
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="step:1;47:17">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="cmd:1;48:18">In the REPL, run <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:3;48:43">dump html</codeph> on your document
            to see the actual HTML structure.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="info:1;50:19">
              <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;51:47">md-validate repl
&gt; load docs/tutorial.md
&gt; dump html</codeblock>
              <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:3;54:18">Confirm that headings are direct children of
              <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:4;55:23">&lt;body&gt;</codeph> with no section wrappers.</p>
            </info>
          </step>
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="step:2;58:17">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="cmd:2;59:18">Rewrite the XPath to use absolute position instead of
            containment.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="info:2;61:19">
              <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:4;62:18">Instead of:</p>
              <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeblock:2;63:47">.//h2[@id='prerequisites']/following-sibling::p[1]</codeblock>
              <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:5;64:18">Use:</p>
              <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeblock:3;65:47">//h2[normalize-space(text())='Prerequisites']</codeblock>
              <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:6;66:18">Checking for the presence of the heading rather than its
              content achieves the same editorial goal without requiring
              containment.</p>
            </info>
          </step>
        </steps>
      </remedy>
    </troubleSolution>

    <troubleSolution class="- topic/bodydiv troubleshooting/troubleSolution " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="troubleSolution:2;75:22">
      <cause id="cause-text-spaces" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/cause " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="cause:2;76:37">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="title:5;77:16">Cause: Whitespace in element text</title>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:7;78:12">XPath text comparisons are exact. A heading with a trailing space
        (<codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;79:18">Prerequisites </codeph>) does not match the predicate
        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:6;80:17">[text()='Prerequisites']</codeph>.</p>
      </cause>
      <remedy id="remedy-text-spaces" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/remedy " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="remedy:2;82:39">
