        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="steps:2;84:16">
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="step:3;85:17">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="cmd:3;86:18">In the REPL, run the query with <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeph:7;86:58">text</codeph> to
            see the exact string the element contains, including any whitespace.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="info:3;88:19">
              <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="codeblock:4;89:47">&gt; query //h2 text
Result: ['Prerequisites ', 'Deploy the app']</codeblock>
              <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="p:8;91:18">Note any trailing spaces in the output.</p>
            </info>
          </step>
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_xpath-wrong-results.dita" xtrc="step:4;94:17">
